translations: （使）现酒窝；做出凹痕；起涟漪（dimple 的现在分词）

sentences.sentence: And the dimpling stream runs laughing by;
sentences.translation: 汩汩的流水笑出了酒窝的细纹；

sentences.sentence: In every dimpling drop I see wild flowers upon the hills.
sentences.translation: 在每滴雨珠中，我看到山上的野花。

sentences.sentence: there are many genes that are already expressed and presented in this dimpling and thickening of the outer layer.
sentences.translation: 在外胚层的凹陷和增厚过程中,表达了很多基因。
